Bisakah kamu berhenti bersikap kekanak-kanakan?

00:20:27.090 --> 00:20:28.260
Memukul tanpa bertanya,

00:20:28.260 --> 00:20:29.190
lalu berpaling?

00:20:29.190 --> 00:20:30.260
Dia lebih dewasa?

00:20:30.690 --> 00:20:31.760
Kalau begitu, pergilah ke dia.

